## @file
#
# This library implements the TCG TSS 2.0 TPM Command Transmission Interface
# (TCTI) API specification. The implementation uses the TCG2 UEFI protocol
# driver to send commands and receive responses from the TPM2 device. The
# TCTI API exposed is then used by higher layers of the TSS2 (like the
# System API) to transport commands and responses as required.
